Class EPPAssemblerException

java.lang.Object
  java.lang.Throwable
      java.lang.Exception
          com.verisign.epp.exception.EPPException
              com.verisign.epp.framework.EPPAssemblerException
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class EPPAssemblerException
extends EPPException

The EPPAssemblerException defines a set of possible exceptions that can be thrown from an EPPAssembler. Static instances of EPPAssemblerExceptions are defined here and should be used by clients of this class. As a general guideline, there is a unique EPPAssemblerException associated with each concrete EPPAssembler class.

Version:
$Revision: 1.2 $
Author:
$Author: jim $
